node.title: Blisstech - NightTripper Project Part 2 The Ship

description.description: Check out this video of the second installment of Otherworld lore to get you psyched for the upcoming release of my graphic novel. Watch this space for updates...

Here's the first lore post for my #otherworld project. The purpose of these are to introduce you to the world and give you some back story before the book is released. Enjoy these during your daily scheduled quarantine

Hey guys! Welcome to the official page for the Otherworld comic. I'm the artist and writer behind this project. Watch this space for upcoming news for our upcoming crowdfunding campaign and release dates for the book and merch. #makingcomics
